travel-net (0.1.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Web UI: Dashboard, WiFi Scan, Configuration, Getting Started wizard
  * AP+STA hybrid mode via hostapd + wpa_supplicant
  * DHCP/DNS via dnsmasq
  * Firewall via nftables (NAT + forwarding)
  * System info: uptime, DHCP clients, reboot
  * NetworkManager and wpa_supplicant backend support

